### ==========================================
### 系统设置模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token（管理员）
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：获取系统设置
GET http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：更新系统设置
PUT http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systemConfig": {
    "enableAI": true
  }
}

### 3. 正常流程：获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:18081/api/admin/users?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 正常流程：获取角色列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 正常流程：创建角色
POST http://localhost:18081/api/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "API_TEST_ROLE",
  "name": "API测试角色",
  "description": "通过API创建的测试角色",
  "dataScope": "SELF",
  "menuPermissions": ["dashboard", "project"]
}

### 6. 正常流程：获取接口权限矩阵
GET http://localhost:18081/api/admin/permissions/endpoints
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 正常流程：获取数据范围配置
GET http://localhost:18081/api/admin/settings/data-scope
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 正常流程：保存部门树
PUT http://localhost:18081/api/admin/settings/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"id":1,"name":"市场部","parentId":null,"sort":1},
  {"id":2,"name":"技术部","parentId":null,"sort":2}
]

### 9. 边界：非管理员访问设置
# @name staffLogin
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "xiaowang",
  "password": "123456"
}

@staffToken = {{staffLogin.response.body.data.token}}

GET http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

### 10. 边界：不存在的角色 ID
GET http://localhost:18081/api/admin/roles/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
